descriptionHtml:
First of all, sorry for my english. Celes is a pretty high elf still keeping (in my opinion) some elf features. I enjoy playing as a high elf and don\'t understand why others dont (or so i read, i don\'t care about their bad reputation lol)
Race: High elf
Level: 1
Location: Riverwood
Main quest: Has just been asked by Ralof\\\'s sister to go to Whiterun
Quests: none taken yet, hasnt talked to anyone yet but the trader in town to sell some stuff
Gold: 901 
Equiped: basic mage gear plus some soldiers\\\'s boots and gauntles, health ring, fire spell and healing spell
Inventory: random ingredients and health, magicka and stamina potions
